  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Vacuum-assisted dressings (V-AD) are effective in treating patients with open chest wounds
      (OCW) and will decrease the time-to-closure of such wounds when compared to a historical
      cohort of patients managed by traditional wound care management.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
